content.description: Self-appointed as a Neo-Neapolitan style pizzeria, this is a bright spot that dons a line of of colorful tiles, red stools, and a blazing open kitchen equipped with—you guessed it—a wood-burning oven. You may even see Chef/owner Matteo Venini manning this mighty machine, as he is known to turn out ...
